            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-334-79L1-line-69" n="69">I ne'er could endure my talent to smother:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-79L1-line-70" n="70">I told you one tale, and I·'ll tell you another.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-79L1-line-71" n="71">A joiner, to fasten a saint in a <hi rend="italics">nitch</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-79L1-line-72" n="72">Bor'd a lage <hi rend="italics">auger-hole</hi> in the image's breech.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-79L1-line-73" n="73">But, finding the <hi rend="italics">statue</hi> to make no complaint,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-79L1-line-74" n="74">He would ne'er be convinced it was a <hi rend="italics">true saint</hi>.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-79L1-line-75" n="75">When the <hi rend="italics">true Wood</hi> arrives, as he soon will, no doubt,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-79L1-line-76" n="76">(For that·'s but a sham <hi rend="italics">Wood</hi> they carry about<note place="foot">·He was frequently burnt in effigy.</note>;)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-79L1-line-77" n="77">What <hi rend="italics">stuff</hi> he is made of you quickly may find,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-79L1-line-78" n="78">If you make the same trial, and <hi rend="italics">bore</hi> him <hi rend="italics">behind</hi>.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-79L1-line-79" n="79">I·'ll hold you a groat, when you <hi rend="italics">wimble</hi> his <hi rend="italics">bum</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-79L1-line-80" n="80">He·'ll bellow as loud as the <hi rend="italics">Devil</hi> in a <hi rend="italics">drum</hi>.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-79L1-line-81" n="81">From me, I declare, you shall have no denial;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-79L1-line-82" n="82">And there can be no harm in making a trial:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-79L1-line-83" n="83">And, when to the joy of your hearts he has roar'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-79L1-line-84" n="84">You may shew him about for a new <hi rend="italics">groaning-board</hi>.</l>
